{"tid":353912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"解放軍運8電子戰飛機環繞台灣飛行","createTime":"2017-08-10T04:12:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-10T04:12:42.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5650ffd0dd94b3578af9ac3a7d96228595228dab","tid":353912,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T04:12:22.000Z","msg":"日本防衛省說，大陸解放軍一架運8電子戰飛機，昨天圍繞台灣飛行。<br />\n<br />\n防衛省統合幕僚監部的公告說，這架運8飛機昨天從西太平洋經宮古海峽飛入東海空域，日方派出戰機緊急升空應對。根據飛行路線圖，這架運8飛機從巴士海峽經西太平洋北上，從東面繞行台灣。<br />\n<br />\n中國國防部早前表示，中國軍機在宮古海峽空域飛行合法正當，今後將根據形勢和任務需要，繼續組織類似遠海訓練，有關方面不必大驚小怪。"},{"pid":"17ade5c6328190663f524b37aee654fe0f44fb62","tid":353912,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T04:12:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1347398-20170810.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1347398-20170810.htm&d=z%2FT0cVt%2BJsczYFWQSvdWqPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=f45cd1cf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1347398-20170810.htm&h=12874d8b\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1347398-20170810.htm</a>"}]}